1. Count the number of patients by each service.
ğğ®ğğ«ğ²: select service, count(name) as total_patients from patients group by service

2. Calculate the average age of patients grouped by service.
ğğ®ğğ«ğ²: select service, AVG(age) as avg_age from patients group by service order by avg_age

3. Find the total number of staff members per role.
ğğ®ğğ«ğ²: select role, COUNT(staff_id) as total from staff group by role order by total desc

